StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetAllEduca.onTier]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SELECT EDUCATION_TIER AS ID, EDUCATION_CODE, TIER_BEGIN_DATE, TIER_END_DATE FROM dbo.EDUCATION_TIER WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE TIER_END_DATE IS NULL OR TIER_END_DATE > GetDate() ORDER BY EDUCATION_CODE, EDUCATION_TIER
